{"word":"ἀνθρακιά","slug":"ἀνθρακιά","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνθρακιά</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἄνθραξ'><el>ἄνθραξ</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a heap of charcoal, hot embers</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>ἀνθρακιᾶς ἄπο</el> hot from <i>the embers</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>black sooty ashes</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}